我们能行, 孩子们来吧

722
00:44:31,980 --> 00:44:32,950
Through.
划

723
00:44:33,080 --> 00:44:34,280
In, through.
破 划

724
00:44:34,480 --> 00:44:36,350
Don't panic, Bobby.
别慌, 鲍比

725
00:44:36,920 --> 00:44:38,120
Don't rush.
不要着急

726
00:44:38,180 --> 00:44:40,280
<i>Cal still showing no signs of slowing down.
加州队仍然没有放缓的迹象</i>

727
00:44:40,420 --> 00:44:42,530
<i>Washington is getting its first taste of competition.</i>
<i>华盛顿队初尝竞争滋味</i>

728
00:44:42,650 --> 00:44:45,010
<i>Something Coach Ulbrickson can hope to build on.</i>
<i>乌尔布里克森教练还可以再接再厉</i>

729
00:44:47,200 --> 00:44:49,190
Through! In, and through!
划 破 划

730
00:44:49,310 --> 00:44:51,210
Push! Push!
推 推

731
00:44:51,560 --> 00:44:53,440
All right, here we go, boys.
好了, 开始吧, 孩子们

732
00:44:53,800 --> 00:44:55,130
Give me 35.
给我 35 拍

733
00:44:55,450 --> 00:44:57,060
Let's show 'em what we got.
让他们看看我们的厉害吧

734
00:44:57,640 --> 00:44:59,870
Build! Build it!
用力 用力

735
00:44:59,970 --> 00:45:02,470
What are they doing? I said let Cal come back to them.
他们在干什么？我说过让加州队走在前面

736
00:45:04,580 --> 00:45:06,650
<i>Now at the halfway mark.</i>
<i>现在赛程过半</i>

737
00:45:07,150 --> 00:45:08,520
The Huskies with a burst.
哈士奇队突然爆发

738
00:45:09,990 --> 00:45:12,540
<i>Just passing the halfway point and Washington is surging.</i>
<i>刚过半程, 华盛顿队就开始发力</i>

739
00:45:12,590 --> 00:45:14,490
Oh, you better be right, Moch.
哦, 你最好是对的, 莫奇

740
00:45:16,290 --> 00:45:17,660
In, through!
破 划

741
00:45:18,400 --> 00:45:20,190
- In, through! <i>- Here they come.</i>
- 破 划 <i>- 他们来了</i>

742
00:45:20,430 --> 00:45:22,030
<i>Here comes Washington.</i>
<i>华盛顿队来了</i>

743
00:45:22,100 --> 00:45:23,290
Eyes up.
抬头

744
00:45:23,500 --> 00:45:25,200
- Eyes up! - Push!
- 抬头 - 推

745
00:45:25,930 --> 00:45:28,000
<i>They're past the three-quarter mark.</i>
<i>他们已经越过了四分之三标志处</i>

746
00:45:28,130 --> 00:45:30,700
<i>Cal and Washington are neck and neck!</i>
<i>加州队和华盛顿队齐头并进！</i>

747
00:45:33,080 --> 00:45:34,210
Go! Row!
加油 划

748
00:45:34,340 --> 00:45:35,970
Stay loose!
放松！

749
00:45:37,260 --> 00:45:39,220
Push! Push!
推 推

750
00:45:39,750 --> 00:45:41,180
<i>Cal is falling back.</i>
<i>加州队正在落后</i>

751
00:45:41,310 --> 00:45:42,520
Let's go!
冲

752
00:45:42,840 --> 00:45:44,370
<i>Washington is picking up the pace!</i>
<i>华盛顿正在加快节奏！</i>

753
00:45:44,490 --> 00:45:45,880
<i>Washington's passing Cal!</i>
<i>华盛顿队超过加州队</i>

754
00:45:46,950 --> 00:45:48,250
And look at this.
看看这个

755
00:45:48,280 --> 00:45:50,270
The Washington boat has taken the lead!
华盛顿队已经取得领先

756
00:45:51,790 --> 00:45:53,030
<i>Washington by half a boat!</i>
<i>华盛顿队领先半条艇身</i>

757
00:45:53,260 --> 00:45:55,060
- Row! Let's go! - Come on!
- 划！我们走 - 来吧

758
00:45:55,430 --> 00:45:56,990
<i>Two hundred meters to go!</i>
<i>还有两百米！</i>

759
00:45:57,200 --> 00:45:59,570
<i>- Washington is pulling ahead!</i> - Twenty more strokes!
<i>- 华盛顿领先！</i> - 再划二十桨！

760
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:01,300
Come on, come on.
加油 加油

761
00:46:03,280 --> 00:46:04,550
Come on! Go!
加油 上

762
00:46:04,610 --> 00:46:06,120
<i>Washington by a full boat!</i>
<i>华盛顿队领先了整条船身</i>

763
00:46:06,710 --> 00:46:09,050
In and through! <i>One hundred meters!</i>
破 划！<i>一百米！</i>

764
00:46:09,180 --> 00:46:11,680
Fifteen more!
还有 15 桨！

765
00:46:13,830 --> 00:46:15,630
Come on! Come on!
加油 加油

766
00:46:16,440 --> 00:46:18,510
Through! Ten more!
蹬！还有十桨

767
00:46:19,970 --> 00:46:21,160
<i>Fifty meters!</i>
<i>五十米！</i>

768
00:46:21,450 --> 00:46:22,740
Fifty meters!
五十米

769
00:46:22,920 --> 00:46:25,300
<i>Washington is going to do it!</i>
<i>华盛顿队要赢了！</i>

770
00:46:26,350 --> 00:46:28,550
You got this! In and through!
你们能行！破 划

771
00:46:29,990 --> 00:46:31,200
Push!
推！

772
00:46:32,470 --> 00:46:33,900
<i>Twenty-five meters!</i>
<i>二十五米！</i>

773
00:46:36,700 --> 00:46:38,470
<i>And there's the flag!</i>
<i>那就是终点</i>

774
00:46:38,550 --> 00:46:40,250
<i>Washington has done it!</i>
<i>华盛顿队做到了！</i>

775
00:46:40,340 --> 00:46:42,740
<i>Washington's junior boat has won their first competition!</i>
<i>华盛顿队初级艇赢得了他们的首场比赛！</i>

776
00:46:42,770 --> 00:46:43,850
Yeah!
耶

777
00:46:43,870 --> 00:46:46,320
<i>What a promising start for these young men!</i>
<i>对于这些年轻人来说, 这是一个多么有希望的开始！</i>

778
00:46:47,320 --> 00:46:48,350
Jesus!
天啊

779
00:46:49,150 --> 00:46:51,720
I got nine seconds under the course record.
我这比赛道记录快了 9 秒

780
00:46:51,910 --> 00:46:52,980
Same.
一样

781
00:46:53,630 --> 00:46:56,230
And the final third is faster than the first.
最后三分之一的速度比一开始还要快

782
00:46:56,880 --> 00:46:58,910
Where the hell did that come from?
到底是从哪里来的力气？

783
00:47:00,490 --> 00:47:02,810
I guess that little runt knew what he was doin'.
我猜那个小矮子知道自己在做什么

784
00:47:04,600 --> 00:47:06,500
- Yeah! - Yeah!
- 好哦 - 好哦

785
00:47:06,580 --> 00:47:07,980
It's all you, boys!
干的漂亮, 孩子们

786
00:47:08,120 --> 00:47:09,150
All you!
你们都是

787
00:47:09,440 --> 00:47:11,550
Yeah!
漂亮

788
00:47:40,400 --> 00:47:41,740
One!
一

789
00:47:41,870 --> 00:47:42,870
Two!
二

790
00:47:43,530 --> 00:47:44,910
Three!
三

791
00:47:53,150 --> 00:47:55,450
I like your hat. Thank you. Thank you.
我喜欢你的帽子 谢谢

792
00:47:56,350 --> 00:47:57,690
Come on!
来吧

793
00:47:58,150 --> 00:47:59,890
Washington!
华盛顿

794
00:48:00,020 --> 00:48:01,080
Come on!
来吧

795
00:48:02,090 --> 00:48:03,560
Oh, my God.
我的天啊

796
00:48:03,900 --> 00:48:04,890
Hi.
你好

797
00:48:05,260 --> 00:48:06,890
I could get used to this.
我可以习惯这样

798
00:48:08,340 --> 00:48:09,840
How did your first win feel?
第一次获胜的感觉如何？

799
00:48:09,960 --> 00:48:10,930
Great.
好极了

800
00:48:11,300 --> 00:48:13,030
Next one's gonna be even faster.
下一次会更快

801
00:48:26,360 --> 00:48:27,720
How did you go so fast?
你怎么划得这么快？

802
00:48:28,250 --> 00:48:29,880
Oh, we just rowed as quick as we could.
哦, 我们就是拼命在划

803
00:48:30,020 --> 00:48:32,550
It must have been hard, even though you're strong.
虽然你很强壮, 但这一定很难

804
00:48:32,680 --> 00:48:33,990
You get tired?
你累吗？

805
00:48:34,550 --> 00:48:36,080
Yeah, yeah, it was pretty rough.
是啊, 是啊, 是挺艰难的

806
00:48:36,920 --> 00:48:38,720
Too tired to go someplace quiet
太累了, 不想去安静的地方

807
00:48:38,750 --> 00:48:40,550
and show me how you did it?
告诉我你是如何做到的吗？

808
00:48:41,820 --> 00:48:43,130
Oh, hell no.
哦, 当然不会

809
00:48:44,740 --> 00:48:46,730
You know, this might make all the times
你知道, 让莫里斯吐在我背上

810
00:48:46,770 --> 00:48:48,970
Morris puked on my back worth it.
那么多次 可能也都值了

811
00:48:49,080 --> 00:48:50,410
I got this today.
我今天收到了这个

812
00:48:50,590 --> 00:48:52,300
Some fellow in a suit just gave it to me.
是一个西装革履的家伙给我的

813
00:48:52,370 --> 00:48:53,840
Said us winning made him so happy, he wanted me to have...
他说我们赢了让他很高兴, 他想让我...

814
00:48:53,890 --> 00:48:55,310
Shoot, we all made him happy, Gordo.
我们都让他很开心, 戈多

815
00:48:55,380 --> 00:48:56,580
Kid in my algebra class
我代数课上的孩子

816
00:48:56,630 --> 00:48:57,820
offered to do my homework for me.
主动要帮我做作业

817
00:48:57,910 --> 00:48:59,420
- I let the sap do it. - You should.
- 我就让他做了 - 应该的

818
00:48:59,460 --> 00:49:00,710
We keep on winnin',
我们继续赢下去

819
00:49:00,930 --> 00:49:02,690
we're gonna have it made in this place.
可能真的会在这里实现的

820
00:49:02,720 --> 00:49:04,950
- You did so good today. - Huh?
- 你今天干得真不错 - 嗯？

821
00:49:06,090 --> 00:49:07,220
I said you did so...
我说你今天...

822
00:49:07,600 --> 00:49:09,090
I said you did so good today.
我说你今天表现得很好

823
00:49:10,080 --> 00:49:11,040
Thank you.
谢谢

824
00:49:11,720 --> 00:49:13,060
It was... It was fun.
这是...很有趣

825
00:49:14,330 --> 00:49:15,300
What?
什么？

826
00:49:17,800 --> 00:49:20,200
Come here. I said it was fun.
过来 我说这很有趣

827
00:49:29,450 --> 00:49:31,410
Do you wanna go someplace quiet?
你想去个安静的地方吗？

828
00:50:12,550 --> 00:50:13,760
Watcha doin'?
你在干什么？

829
00:50:14,270 --> 00:50:15,240
I'm watching.
我就看看

830
00:50:15,630 --> 00:50:17,260
Why aren't you talking to anybody?
你为什么不跟任何人说话？

831
00:50:17,730 --> 00:50:19,090
I'm not much of a talker.
我不太爱说话

832
00:50:19,230 --> 00:50:20,260
Ah.
啊

833
00:50:21,270 --> 00:50:22,670
Hey, look over there.
嘿, 看那边

834
00:50:24,640 --> 00:50:26,830
You see that beanpole in the glasses?
看到那个戴眼镜的豆芽菜了吗？

835
00:50:27,620 --> 00:50:28,820
Yeah.
是啊

836
00:50:29,270 --> 00:50:30,770
He's studying Latin.
他在学拉丁语

837
00:50:32,450 --> 00:50:33,880
- Oh. - Latin.
- 哦 - 拉丁语

838
00:50:34,400 --> 00:50:35,960
You don't have to say much.
你不必说太多

839
00:50:36,500 --> 00:50:38,030
Listen, Hume.
听着, 休谟

840
00:50:38,240 --> 00:50:41,380
Tonight, not tomorrow night, or next week.
今晚, 不是明晚, 也不是下周

841
00:50:41,460 --> 00:50:43,470
Tonight is your best shot.
今晚是你最好的机会

842
00:50:45,520 --> 00:50:46,780
You go on. I think I'm okay.
你继续 我想我没事

843
00:50:46,970 --> 00:50:48,810
Christ sake.
看在上帝的份上

844
00:51:08,870 --> 00:51:10,330
Hey, listen up!
嘿, 听好了

845
00:51:11,210 --> 00:51:13,220
We got a musician in our midst.
我们中间有一位音乐家

846
00:51:13,500 --> 00:51:14,890
With a little encouragement,
稍加鼓励

847
00:51:15,510 --> 00:51:17,640
we might just get him to give us some live music.
可能会让他给我们带来一些现场音乐

848
00:51:17,690 --> 00:51:18,960
Don Hume!
唐·休姆

849
00:51:20,150 --> 00:51:21,980
Get up here. Get up here.
快上来 快上来

850
00:51:22,120 --> 00:51:24,030
Come on, Don!
来吧, 唐！

851
00:51:24,160 --> 00:51:25,630
No. No.
不 不

852
00:51:25,760 --> 00:51:28,030
- Hey, watch out. - No, no, no, no, no.
- 嘿, 小心点 - 不, 不, 不

853
00:51:29,640 --> 00:51:30,880
Bobby, get the stool.
鲍比, 拿凳子来

854
00:51:31,470 --> 00:51:32,630
The piano man.
钢琴师

855
00:51:32,870 --> 00:51:34,770
John, John, John
约翰, 约翰, 约翰

856
00:51:34,970 --> 00:51:36,930
- No, no, no. - There we go.
- 不, 不, 不 - 到了

857
00:51:37,360 --> 00:51:39,180
All ready for you there, <i>maestro.</i>
一切准备就绪, <i>大师.</i>

858
00:51:41,340 --> 00:51:43,240
Let's hear it for Don!
让我们为唐鼓掌！

859
00:51:43,330 --> 00:51:44,270
Don Hume.
唐·休姆

860
00:51:44,410 --> 00:51:46,040
Come on, Don!
来吧, 唐！

861
00:51:50,120 --> 00:51:51,480
We know you can do it.
我们知道你能做到

862
00:51:55,920 --> 00:51:57,730
- Come on, Don. - Come on, Donnie.
- 来吧 唐 - 加油 唐尼

863
00:52:24,580 --> 00:52:26,510
I don't think that I should be here.
我觉得我不应该在这

864
00:52:34,780 --> 00:52:36,410
He can't be in here.
他不能进来

865
00:52:36,600 --> 00:52:37,770
Oh, shut up, Carolyn.
闭嘴 卡洛琳

866
00:52:37,810 --> 00:52:39,870
I saw you smoking at your window last week.
上周我看见你在窗前抽烟

867
00:52:43,780 --> 00:52:45,330
It was too loud in there.
那边太吵了

868
00:52:45,350 --> 00:52:47,630
Yeah. People are happy. They're having fun.
对 大家很快乐 他们玩得很开心

869
00:52:48,070 --> 00:52:49,810
Yeah, because of you.
对, 因为你

870
00:52:53,910 --> 00:52:55,170
Okay, I'm changing.
好吧, 我要换衣服了

871
00:52:56,390 --> 00:52:57,510
Eyes on the wall.
眼睛看着墙壁

872
00:52:57,700 --> 00:52:58,900
Right.
好

873
00:53:04,640 --> 00:53:06,380
Did you know you were gonna win?
你知道自己会赢吗？

874
00:53:06,610 --> 00:53:08,570
No. My arms, they were shaking.
不, 我的手臂在颤抖

875
00:53:08,700 --> 00:53:09,940
I was so nervous.
我太紧张了

876
00:53:10,100 --> 00:53:11,970
We were all screaming so loud.
我们都在大声尖叫

877
00:53:12,170 --> 00:53:14,030
The radio said it was the fastest ever.
广播说这是有史以来最快的一次

878
00:53:14,100 --> 00:53:15,940
Yeah, that's what Coach told us.
对, 教练是这么告诉我们的

879
00:53:20,200 --> 00:53:22,030
I bet you win every race.
我打赌你们每场都能赢

880
00:53:33,010 --> 00:53:35,510
Just don't get all stuck-up and everything.
只要不自命不凡就好

881
00:53:43,270 --> 00:53:46,750
I just kept that in case I ever ran into you again.
我把它留着, 以防再遇到你

882
00:53:49,100 --> 00:53:50,560
And had to, um...
不得不...

883
00:53:52,130 --> 00:53:55,730
prove that you had that crush on me, like I said.
证明你暗恋过我, 就像我说的那样

884
00:54:19,320 --> 00:54:21,420
Miss Simdars, open this door.
西姆达斯小姐, 开门

885
00:54:22,050 --> 00:54:23,380
You... You should go.
你...你该走了

886
00:54:23,500 --> 00:54:25,400
You should go. You need to go. You need to go.
你该走了 你必须走了 你必须走了

887
00:54:25,560 --> 00:54:28,030
Miss Simdars, open this door right now, young lady.
西姆达斯小姐, 马上开门, 小姐

888
00:54:28,160 --> 00:54:30,060
If you have a male visitor in there,
如果里面有男性访客

889
00:54:30,190 --> 00:54:32,090
well, you know the consequences.
那么, 你知道后果是什么

890
00:54:32,190 --> 00:54:34,330
One minute!
一分钟

891
00:54:34,710 --> 00:54:35,780
- What? - Is that too far?
- 什么 - 太高了吗？

892
00:54:35,800 --> 00:54:37,270
- No. - You're fine.
- 不 - 那很好

893
00:54:37,410 --> 00:54:38,340
Miss Simdars!
西姆达斯小姐

894
00:54:38,910 --> 00:54:40,600
<i>Ain't we got fun?</i>
<i>我们玩得开心吗？</i>

895
00:54:41,240 --> 00:54:43,710
<i>Tax collector's getting closer</i>
<i>收税员越来越近了</i>

896
00:54:43,850 --> 00:54:45,890
<i>Still, we got fun</i>
<i>尽管如此, 我们还是很开心</i>

897
00:54:46,520 --> 00:54:48,080
<i>There's nothing surer</i>
<i>没有比这更确定的了</i>

898
00:54:48,410 --> 00:54:51,180
<i>The rich get rich and the poor get poorer</i>
<i>富者愈富, 穷者愈穷</i>

899
00:54:51,320 --> 00:54:53,820
<i>In the meantime, in between time</i>
<i>同时, 此时</i>

900
00:54:53,950 --> 00:54:56,520
<i>Ain't we got fun?</i>
<i>我们玩得开心吗？</i>

901
00:55:02,930 --> 00:55:04,130
Well done!
干得好

902
00:55:04,270 --> 00:55:06,160
Okay! Yeah!
好 好

903
00:55:10,200 --> 00:55:11,870
Don Hume, ladies and gentlemen.
唐·休姆, 女士们先生们

904
00:55:32,860 --> 00:55:34,760
- Harvard, Yale? - Mm-hmm.
- 哈佛 耶鲁？- 嗯

905
00:55:35,430 --> 00:55:38,900
Both have put up times we haven't gotten close to.
两队的成绩都是我们无法企及的

