Bobby, not another Poughkeepsie.
鲍比, 别再来波基普西那招了

1630
01:40:08,820 --> 01:40:10,250
They won't fade like Cal,
它们不会像加州队那样后程乏力的

1631
01:40:10,280 --> 01:40:12,010
so never let them get more than two lengths up.
所以绝不能让他们领先超过两个艇位

1632
01:40:12,220 --> 01:40:14,210
Fellas, you've earned this.
伙计们, 这是你们应得的

1633
01:40:15,020 --> 01:40:17,590
They don't give gold medals for style.
他们不会为风格颁发金牌

1634
01:40:17,890 --> 01:40:20,260
<i>All that matters is how fast you are on the water.</i>
<i>唯一重要的是你们在水上的速度有多快</i>

1635
01:40:21,060 --> 01:40:22,670
<i>And nobody here is faster.</i>
<i>这里没人比你们更快</i>

1636
01:40:32,140 --> 01:40:33,410
Legs through!
蹬腿！

1637
01:40:33,980 --> 01:40:35,670
<i>And the Americans are already leading</i>
<i>美国人已经领先</i>

1638
01:40:35,760 --> 01:40:37,230
<i>by half a boat over Great Britain</i>
<i>大不列颠半个艇位</i>

1639
01:40:37,340 --> 01:40:38,740
<i>and looking for more.</i>
<i>优势还在变大</i>

1640
01:40:38,820 --> 01:40:40,920
<i>Followed by France and Czechoslovakia.
法国和捷克斯洛伐克紧随其后</i>

1641
01:40:45,540 --> 01:40:48,540
In, through! In, through!
破 划！破 划！

1642
01:40:49,680 --> 01:40:51,380
<i>Stroke Ran Laurie</i>
<i>领桨员冉·劳里</i</i>

1643
01:40:51,410 --> 01:40:52,880
<i>is digging furiously for the British boat.</i>
<i>正在疯狂地挖掘英国艇的速度</i>

1644
01:40:52,930 --> 01:40:54,230
<i>But the Americans</i>
<i>但是美国人</i>

1645
01:40:54,250 --> 01:40:56,340
<i>are pouring it on now, extending their lead.</i>
<i>现在正在大举进攻, 扩大领先优势</i>

1646
01:40:56,950 --> 01:40:59,280
Eyes up. In, through!
抬头 破 划

1647
01:40:59,870 --> 01:41:01,140
And through!
划

1648
01:41:01,540 --> 01:41:03,160
<i>And with only 100 meters to go, </i>
<i>只剩 100 米了</i>

1649
