<i>Deutschland! Deutschland!</i>
<i>德国！德国！</i>

1734
01:47:13,510 --> 01:47:18,210
<i>Deutschland! Deutschland! Deutschland! Deutschland!</i>
<i>德国！德国！德国！德国！</i>

1735
01:47:18,350 --> 01:47:20,910
<i>Deutschland! Deutschland! Deutschland! Deutschland!</i>
<i>德国！德国！德国！德国！</i>

1736
01:47:21,050 --> 01:47:22,890
<i>Deutschland! Deutschland!</i>
<i>德国！德国！</i>

1737
01:47:23,020 --> 01:47:26,620
<i>Deutschland! Deutschland! Deutschland! Deutschland!</i>
<i>德国！德国！德国！德国！</i>

1738
01:47:26,750 --> 01:47:28,920
<i>Deutschland! Deutschland!</i>
<i>德国！德国！</i>

1739
01:47:44,500 --> 01:47:45,960
Don, you okay?
唐, 你还好吗？

1740
01:47:46,450 --> 01:47:48,920
You got this, Don, all right?
你能行的, 唐, 好吗？

1741
01:47:54,990 --> 01:47:56,600
Hey, what'd he say?
嘿, 他说什么？

1742
01:47:58,250 --> 01:47:59,650
All right. Come on, let's win this.
好吧 来吧, 让我们赢下这一场

1743
01:47:59,780 --> 01:48:00,950
Oars ready.
桨准备好了

1744
01:48:07,030 --> 01:48:08,090
Come on.
来吧

1745
01:48:09,200 --> 01:48:10,800
All right, we got two lengths of wind
好吧, 我们有两段风

1746
